Kali Rocha https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kali_Rocha 0 Kali Michele Rocha (born December 5, 1971) is an American actress. She is known for portraying Karen Rooney, the mother of four Rooney children and school's vice principal, in the Disney Channel sitcom, Liv and Maddie.
